{"tid":981619,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最醜老虎悲憤撞牆！ 揭背後血淋淋真相","createTime":"2019-01-14T12:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T14:00:13.000Z","uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"738d2d4d9482d0c8426ebede9ddcae68e850210c","tid":981619,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/14/201923_a58d4b71d866710b1d1262bb4707dcd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F201923_a58d4b71d866710b1d1262bb4707dcd6.png&h=2e5955f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/14/201924_4c3cde4bb3c6f2c33c2432d7b54d6881.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2F201924_4c3cde4bb3c6f2c33c2432d7b54d6881.png&h=fd4ea585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老虎向來有百獸之王美譽，不僅在動物園和馬戲團裡相當受歡迎，尤其又以顏色稀有的白老虎最具代表性。然而，有黑心商人為了斂財，不惜利用近親繁殖手段來獲得更多白老虎，以致生下有生理缺陷的白老虎。號稱「世界最醜老虎」的美國白老虎肯尼（Kenny）就是血淋淋的實例！<br />\n <br />\n據《太陽報》報導，這隻白虎肯尼因為近親繁殖的關係長得其貌不揚，2歲時就被棄養，幸好當時「松脂溪野生動物保護所」（Turpentine Creek Wildlife Refuge）緊急收養，才讓牠撿回一命。肯尼不僅罹患唐氏症，臉部幾乎毀容，還有著先天的短鼻、大臉，以及排列不整齊的牙齒。<br />\n <br />\n該動物保護所的保育員麥科邁克（Emily McCormack）表示，「肯尼曾經用牠的臉去撞牆」，並透露肯尼被保護所救下後，飽受遺傳性疾病痛苦，不但經常生病，還有脊椎側彎、關節發育不良等問題，僅活10年便逝世。相較於正常老虎長達25年的壽命，令人感到相當心疼。<br />\n <br />\n保護所也指出，大多數的白老虎是因為人類的貪婪，透過近親繁殖方式讓老虎生下的物種。為了推出1隻能登台的漂亮老虎，可能得一次培育了30隻，但其中只有1隻可以中選，其牠的可能就丟掉，或是安樂死，行逕非常殘忍。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，「白虎」是孟加拉虎的1種變種，原產於中國雲南、緬甸、印度及孟加拉，由於顏色特殊又有極高的觀賞價值，也成為商人眼中斂財的工具，若以走私方式買賣，每隻小白虎的價格高達3萬英鎊（約120萬元新台幣）。"},{"pid":"089d4223a92ac05cfea8fc1037b7a66d72b4018e","tid":981619,"uid":185780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"第二張睇落幾得意"},{"pid":"db6ab9a5dfc90ca559e359e2b833c0ee9a6ddd7f","tid":981619,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"極高的觀賞價值<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec5be1ec44614b32b2067dbe2c51cb87f7cee4d","tid":981619,"uid":6446,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"錢7。。。"},{"pid":"097fcfdbd35026725132415688f06e4b8a8abd08","tid":981619,"uid":54,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ec5be1ec44614b32b2067dbe2c51cb87f7cee4d","tid":981619,"uid":6446,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"錢7。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"我都想講  好似。。。。"},{"pid":"d9abc4c6bf8bab5387c7857b4161cafc7bca002c","tid":981619,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6ec5be1ec44614b32b2067dbe2c51cb87f7cee4d","tid":981619,"uid":6446,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:21:48.000Z","msg":"錢7。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"33c2aa0555bfbc6122874ac8b45ee5dff2905032","tid":981619,"uid":31765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"劉江華..."},{"pid":"7343f07f6b2b0b5bef660d0d0b47361f0f86f31d","tid":981619,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"第一時間已經諗起錢七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bede665632bc17152dfe837bd234275006c41b32","tid":981619,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"另一篇文先話佢唔係唐氏症, 仲話老虎唔可能有唐氏症"},{"pid":"8ac0f04a5bb43536e1294d827147fbf76698e954","tid":981619,"uid":32407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:25:46.000Z","msg":"睇片都係鐘意睇白虎多啲"},{"pid":"7adc9ef412552dc612b0bef7d501de4f81220021","tid":981619,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c2aa0555bfbc6122874ac8b45ee5dff2905